<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='394109' id='t-394109'>Without them, it's going to be a problem.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='396844' id='t-396844'>But most bats are voracious insect predators.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='402366' id='t-402366'>It's been estimated in the U.S., in a tiny colony</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='405242' id='t-405242'>of big brown bats, that they will feed</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='407393' id='t-407393'>on over a million insects a year,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='410963' id='t-410963'>and in the United States of America, right now</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='413906' id='t-413906'>bats are being threatened by a disease known as white-nose syndrome.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='417247' id='t-417247'>It's working its way slowly across the U.S. and wiping out</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='420487' id='t-420487'>populations of bats, and scientists have estimated</span>
